---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import LandingSection from '../layouts/LandingSection.astro';
import ResumeHeader from '../layouts/ResumeHeader.astro';
import Contact from '../components/Contact.svelte';
---

<Layout title="n4xo">
	<main>
		<div id="welcome" class="flex justify-center items-center h-screen">
			<div>
				<h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl md:leading-tight lg:text-8xl lg:leading-none xl:text-9xl">Hi!</h1>
				<h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-4xl md:leading-tight lg:text-5xl lg:leading-none xl:text-6.5xl">Welcome to my website.</h2>
				<a href="#about" class="text-n4xo-beige dark:text-n4xo-beige-dark hover:text-n4xo-brown dark:hover:text-n4xo-brown-dark text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6.5xl font-extrabold lg:leading-tight">-></a>
			</div>
		</div>
		<LandingSection title="About me" id="about">
			<div class="flex flex-col xl:flex-row gap-5">
				<div>
					<p class="leading-tight text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl 2xl:text-4xl mb-[20px]">Hey! I'm Nacho (n4xo), a passionate full-stack engineer specializing in backend development.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="leading-relaxed text-l 2xl:text-xl mb-[20px]">I graduated with a degree in Computer Science from the University of Málaga, and I've been honing my skills as a software engineer for nearly two years. My professional journey includes optimizing database pipelines, leading chatbot integrations, and automating processes to enhance efficiency.</p>
					<br>
					<p class="leading-relaxed text-l 2xl:text-xl mb-[20px]">I thrive in environments where I can learn and apply new technologies. Currently, I work with Node.js and TypeScript but have a deep love for Go, particularly with the Fiber framework. I'm also diving into Svelte for front-end development and have my sights set on mastering Rust soon.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</LandingSection>
		<LandingSection title="Projects" id="projects">
			<div class="flex flex-col xl:flex-row gap-5">
				<div>
					<p class="leading-tight text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl 2xl:text-4xl mb-[20px]">Here are some of the projects I've worked on recently:</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="leading-relaxed text-l 2xl:text-xl mb-[20px]">- <a href="https://github.com/n4xo-dev/n4xo.com" class="text-n4xo-beige hover:text-n4xo-brown dark:text-n4xo-beige-dark dark:hover:text-n4xo-brown-dark font-bold">n4xo.com</a>: My personal website built with Astro, Svelte, and Tailwind CSS.</p>
					<p class="leading-relaxed text-l 2xl:text-xl mb-[20px]">- <a href="https://github.com/n4xo-dev/solidurls" class="text-n4xo-beige hover:text-n4xo-brown dark:text-n4xo-beige-dark dark:hover:text-n4xo-brown-dark font-bold">SolidURLs</a>: A URL shortener built with Node.js, TypeScript, and NestJS.</p>
					<p class="leading-relaxed text-l 2xl:text-xl mb-[20px]">- <a href="https://github.com/n4xo-dev/api-wars" class="text-n4xo-beige hover:text-n4xo-brown dark:text-n4xo-beige-dark dark:hover:text-n4xo-brown-dark font-bold">API Wars</a>: My senior thesis project, a comparative analysis between API paradigms, namely REST, GraphQL, and gRPC. I built a social network app backend with Go for each paradigm and compared their performance.</p>
					<p class="leading-relaxed text-l 2xl:text-xl mb-[20px]">- <a href="https://github.com/Cyber-Punk-REAS/the_project" class="text-n4xo-beige hover:text-n4xo-brown dark:text-n4xo-beige-dark dark:hover:text-n4xo-brown-dark font-bold">Cyber Punk REAS</a>: A college project where we built a web app to simulate how the spread of the COVID-19 virus changed in different regions depending on the policies adopted using Java and Spring Boot.</p>
					<p class="leading-relaxed text-l 2xl:text-xl mb-[20px]">- <a href="https://github.com/Solidform-labs/newsletter" class="text-n4xo-beige hover:text-n4xo-brown dark:text-n4xo-beige-dark dark:hover:text-n4xo-brown-dark font-bold">Newsletter</a>: A simple newsletter subscription service built with Go.</p>
					<p class="leading-relaxed text-l 2xl:text-xl mb-[20px]">- <a href="https://github.com/Soft-Coders/SIInt" class="text-n4xo-beige hover:text-n4xo-brown dark:text-n4xo-beige-dark dark:hover:text-n4xo-brown-dark font-bold">SoftCoders</a>: A college project where we built a web app for a FinTech (Ebury) usign Java EE.</p>
					<p class="leading-relaxed text-l 2xl:text-xl mb-[20px]">- <a href="https://github.com/n4xo-dev/geneticSudoku" class="text-n4xo-beige hover:text-n4xo-brown dark:text-n4xo-beige-dark dark:hover:text-n4xo-brown-dark font-bold">Genetic Sudoku</a>: A genetic algorithm to solve Sudoku puzzles built with Java.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</LandingSection>
		<LandingSection title="Resume" id="resume">
			<div>
				<h2 class="leading-tight text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl 2xl:text-4xl mb-[20px] underline">Professional experience</h2>
				<ResumeHeader position='Backend Software Engineer' company='Bizaway' link='https://bizaway.com/en/' date='Nov 2023 - Present'/>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-5">
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl">Optimized DB pipelines, lowering the processing time from 30 seconds to under 400ms.</li>
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl">Contributed to the core code base and created microservices to integrate with third-party providers.</li>
				</ul>
				<ResumeHeader position='Full Stack Automation Engineer' company='Ebury' link='https://ebury.com/' date='Jul 2023 - Nov 2023'/>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-5">
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl">Led the EburyGPT BPA integration, allowing Ebury employees to use our services through the EburyGPT chatbot.</li>
				</ul>
				<ResumeHeader position='Junior Full Stack Automation Engineer' company='Ebury' link='https://ebury.com/' date='Jan 2023 - Jul 2023'/>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-5">
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl">Helped fulfill regulatory obligations by developing an automated microservices process to regularly back up over 26,000 files from Google Drive to a Google Cloud Storage bucket.</li>
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl">Facilitated employees' performance analysis by creating a tool to extract tasks' metadata from all teams in Jira.</li>
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl">Improved developer experience in our team by creating Google Apps Script libraries for commonly used APIs and a Node.js library to authenticate Google API libraries using impersonation (domain-wide delegation).</li>
				</ul>
				<ResumeHeader position='Part-time Full Stack Automation Engineer' company='Ebury' link='https://ebury.com/' date='Aug 2022 - Jan 2023'/>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-5">
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl">Increased consistency on Ebury's infrastructure reconciling Google Workspace Admin and HiBob's data for over 1,600 employees by creating a synchronization cronjob using their APIs and “exploiting” Google Apps Script Web Apps, incurring no cost.</li>
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl">Created a new documentation system for our team using Docsify, improving team collaboration.</li>
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl">Reduced HR and Service Desk's workload by automating employee onboarding on Jira, Vonage, and Fenergo.</li>
				</ul>
				<ResumeHeader position='Paintball Instructor' company='Paintball Mountain' link='https://www.paintballmountain.es/' date='Oct 2021 - Apr 2022'/>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-5">
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl">Honed interpersonal and sales skills by instructing clients on safe paintball practices, supervising gameplay, and successfully upselling reloads, showcasing an ability to understand and cater to client needs effectively.</li>
				<h2 class="leading-tight text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl 2xl:text-4xl mt-[20px] mb-[20px] underline">Education</h2>
				<ResumeHeader position="Bachelor's Degree in Computer Science" company='Universidad de Málaga' link='https://www.uma.es/' date='2024'/>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-5">
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl"><strong>Honors</strong>: Introduction to Software Engineering 10, Computer Structure 9.9, Computer Technology 9.7</li>
				</ul>
				<ResumeHeader position='Enxtension Course on Deep Learning and CUDA' company='Universidad de Málaga' link='https://www.uma.es/' date='2021'/>
				<h2 class="leading-tight text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl 2xl:text-4xl mt-[20px] mb-[20px] underline">Skills</h2>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-5">
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl"><strong>Programming Languages</strong>: TypeScript, JavaScript, Go, Python, SQL, Java, C, HTML, CSS.</li>
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl"><strong>Web Dev</strong>: Node.js, Express, Fiber, REST, GraphQL, gRPC, PostgreSQL, MongoDB Redis, Docker, Apps Script.</li>
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl"><strong>Frontend</strong>: Svelte, Tailwind CSS, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Astro.</li>
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl"><strong>Google Cloud Platform</strong>: Functions, Application Integration, Secret Manager, Workflows, Storage, Run.</li>
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl"><strong>Testing</strong>: Jest, Playwright, Postman, k6.</li>
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl"><strong>Miscellaneous</strong>: Jira, Git, GitHub, Google Workspace, Airtable.</li>
					<li class="leading-snug text-l 2xl:text-xl"><strong>Languages</strong>: English Cambridge C1, Spanish native.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</LandingSection>
		<LandingSection title="Blog" id="blog">
			<div class="flex flex-col xl:flex-row gap-5">
				<div class="flex-1">
					<p class="leading-tight text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl 2xl:text-4xl mb-[20px]">Check out my latest online rants in my blog.</p>
					<p class="leading-relaxed text-l 2xl:text-xl mb-[20px]">Explore thought-provoking articles, coding tutorials, and unique perspectives on technology and productivity.</p>
          <p class="mt-10"><a href="https://medium.com/@n4xo" target="_blank" class="bg-n4xo-beige dark:bg-n4xo-beige-dark text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-n4xo-beige dark:focus:ring-n4xo-beige-dark hover:bg-n4xo-brown dark:hover:bg-n4xo-brown-dark">Check it out</a></p>
				</div>
				<div class="flex-1 gradient-mask relative -z-10">
					<img src="blog.png" alt="Blog" class="w-full h-auto my-10">
				</div>
			</div>
		</LandingSection>
		<LandingSection title="Contact" id="contact">
			<Contact client:load/>
		</LandingSection>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.gradient-mask img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0,0,0,1), rgba(0,0,0,0));
    mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0,0,0,1), rgba(0,0,0,0));
}
</style>